    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "There are a couple of ways to generate the hash, can use either of them\r\n\r\n1. `nix-prefetch-git https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf-go --rev v1.30.0`\r\n2.  Run `nix-shell` with `sha256 = \"\";` this will fail to load the shell and output the required hash in the log as seen in the image, use that\r\n\r\n<img width=\"917\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a07c7032-3a02-4103-87e8-39ccf5afb40d\">\r\n",
    "commit_id": "c86ca8607b4a0be6030419a744ee0c5df3f87a63",
